- Hey.
- Hey.

47:48.958 --> 47:51.125
Mom, would you put her
back to bed for me?

47:51.208 --> 47:52.833
- I gotta...
- Who's at the door?

47:52.916 --> 47:54.333
Never mind that.
I got it.

47:54.416 --> 47:57.541
Honey, Grandma's gonna
put you back to bed.

47:57.625 --> 47:59.583
I'm just gonna go outside
for a minute, okay?

47:59.666 --> 48:02.416
- Okay.
- Okay.

48:02.500 --> 48:04.416
[Cecilia] Come on.

48:06.791 --> 48:09.333
Luke, it's 1:00 in the morning.

48:12.708 --> 48:15.208
Look, I don't know what
you're hoping to find out here.

48:22.416 --> 48:24.000
Luke, come on.

48:26.875 --> 48:29.083
- [Luke] Can you open these up?
- [Perry] Why? What is it you...

48:29.166 --> 48:31.125
[Luke] Just open
the damn doors, Perry.

48:31.208 --> 48:33.125
If Rhett's in there,
he's trashed.

48:33.208 --> 48:35.333
I'll tell you that.

48:35.375 --> 48:37.250
[sighs deeply]

48:37.333 --> 48:39.666
[doors rattle]

48:42.708 --> 48:44.291
Gotta go back to the house

48:44.375 --> 48:46.416
- and get the keys
for the other side.
- [Luke scoffs]

48:47.750 --> 48:49.500
No.

48:50.833 --> 48:53.375
I think we're getting in
right now.

48:57.583 --> 48:58.833
[grunting]

49:00.875 --> 49:03.583
Guys! Knock it off!

49:08.708 --> 49:11.750
[hoofbeats thudding]

49:13.458 --> 49:15.791
[thunder crashes]

49:18.041 --> 49:21.500
[Billy] Luke, might want
to have a look at this.

49:27.666 --> 49:29.458
Looks like somebody's
out riding.

49:29.541 --> 49:30.791
What? No, you idiot.

49:30.875 --> 49:32.875
That's obviously from earlier.

49:34.750 --> 49:37.375
Seems pretty fresh to me.

49:44.708 --> 49:47.583
[horse snorting]

49:47.666 --> 49:49.625
♪ ♪

